Package tests

Class StatisticsOld

  • java.lang.Object
    • tests.StatisticsOld
  • Deprecated. 
    this class is for testing (tuning up)

    public class StatisticsOld
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains methods that can be used to compute statistics about the run of the algorithm, does not support multithreading, only 1 executive thread can be set in the configuration. Every block whose duration is measured is placed between a pair of functions: "start" and "end".
